{"tid":1070351,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人入左醫院，坐左成日等佢做完手術，返到屋企發現唔見左銀包","createTime":"2019-03-20T14:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T04:25:07.000Z","uid":73338,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"452f6610ebf2a343e0965c99f5caf500ce46120f","tid":1070351,"uid":73338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:50:12.000Z","msg":"一點幾聽到醫院電話，醫生要即刻見屋企人<br />\n仆到過去話要即刻做手術<br />\n咁為有坐係A1病房門口等，等到推左入手術個面就去食啲野，因為醫生講唔到個手術要做幾耐。<br />\n去左7-11買完野食就去左員工餐廳到坐住等⋯<br />\n等到七點護士打黎話做完，推左去ICU。<br />\n入到ICU醫生簡單交愈完就話走得⋯話暫時穩定叫我地走<br />\n<br />\n搞完成日，返到屋企發現個銀包唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人係伊莉沙白醫院<br />\nA1門口附近既櫈<br />\n7-11到A座<br />\n員工餐廳出面位置<br />\n或者A座樓梯<br />\n見到一個啡色銀包，入面有銀行卡，信用卡同少少澳紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錢唔緊要，我想要返啲卡同銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n電話：62334491 <br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7cf2eacb93aaae288a219e0102019945429d973","tid":1070351,"uid":62061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"打去保安控制室未？"},{"pid":"5cb6dde713aa9330ba59f3247ee35144d963da28","tid":1070351,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:53:59.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"1f04f1057ad5082f7327dfdd79a67368ba3f4cda","tid":1070351,"uid":42625,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:56:11.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n另外希望你屋企人早日康復"},{"pid":"28adb4fc826e809b5b452401a7317940bb3541e3","tid":1070351,"uid":228989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T15:03:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29f2d3d1299ebda63b65b4da84c589b400af5e17","tid":1070351,"uid":73338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c7cf2eacb93aaae288a219e0102019945429d973","tid":1070351,"uid":62061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"打去保安控制室未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"未，諗住聽日先去醫院搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇化左，依家同聽日去醫院又有咩分別<br />\n希望執到既淨係拎走啲錢，比返個銀包我<br />\n我已經好多事，唔想連卡都要再整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcec11959d32bb7074ee6d971dc814dacc157914","tid":1070351,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"16dfde2374410f8b8933ee12907a709c6a2f80da","tid":1070351,"uid":73338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f04f1057ad5082f7327dfdd79a67368ba3f4cda","tid":1070351,"uid":42625,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:56:11.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n另外希望你屋企人早日康復"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T15:08:07.000Z","msg":"有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我前幾日先返香港，見佢都好地地<br />\n昨日話肚痛痛到入醫院，住左晚<br />\n今日就話要即刻做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e997f6e47c2277413f0e5f2360f72f246ef7f0f8","tid":1070351,"uid":62061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29f2d3d1299ebda63b65b4da84c589b400af5e17","tid":1070351,"uid":73338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c7cf2eacb93aaae288a219e0102019945429d973","tid":1070351,"uid":62061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"打去保安控制室未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"未，諗住聽日先去醫院搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇化左，依家同聽日去醫院又有咩分別<br />\n希望執到既淨係拎走啲錢，比返個銀包我<br />\n我已經好多事，唔想連卡都要再整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T15:08:29.000Z","msg":"24小時控制室都會有人<br />\n試過第二間醫院唔見野打去搵得返<br />\n你打去間醫院叫佢幫你飛線去控制室就得"},{"pid":"6057695eaf99ef314f760beae0b3d8f78004beeb","tid":1070351,"uid":208894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T15:14:35.